					<description><![CDATA[The trouble with teaching particle physics is that students start out thinking that the standard model looks like this when it&#8217;s really more like this I hope this clarifies the situation.]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[
<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The trouble with teaching particle physics is that students start out thinking that the <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Standard_Model">standard model</a> looks like this</p>


<div class="wp-block-image">
<figure class="aligncenter size-large"><a href="https://telescoper.blog/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/2c70e6d5c36be4979a8f1be0e10d3810.jpg"><img width="700" height="526" data-attachment-id="81918" data-permalink="https://telescoper.blog/2026/02/16/the-trouble-with-teaching-particle-physics/2c70e6d5c36be4979a8f1be0e10d3810/" data-orig-file="https://telescoper.blog/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/2c70e6d5c36be4979a8f1be0e10d3810.jpg" data-orig-size="700,526" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}" data-image-title="2c70e6d5c36be4979a8f1be0e10d3810" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://telescoper.blog/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/2c70e6d5c36be4979a8f1be0e10d3810.jpg?w=300" data-large-file="https://telescoper.blog/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/2c70e6d5c36be4979a8f1be0e10d3810.jpg?w=450" src="https://telescoper.blog/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/2c70e6d5c36be4979a8f1be0e10d3810.jpg?w=700" alt="" class="wp-image-81918" srcset="https://telescoper.blog/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/2c70e6d5c36be4979a8f1be0e10d3810.jpg 700w, https://telescoper.blog/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/2c70e6d5c36be4979a8f1be0e10d3810.jpg?w=150 150w, https://telescoper.blog/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/2c70e6d5c36be4979a8f1be0e10d3810.jpg?w=300 300w" sizes="(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px" /></a></figure>
</div>


<p class="wp-block-paragraph">when it&#8217;s really more like this</p>


<div class="wp-block-image">
<figure class="aligncenter size-large"><a href="https://telescoper.blog/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/s7gjcutw88o71.jpg"><img width="450" height="542" data-attachment-id="81912" data-permalink="https://telescoper.blog/2026/02/16/the-trouble-with-teaching-particle-physics/s7gjcutw88o71/" data-orig-file="https://telescoper.blog/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/s7gjcutw88o71.jpg" data-orig-size="1080,1301" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="s7gjcutw88o71" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://telescoper.blog/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/s7gjcutw88o71.jpg?w=249" data-large-file="https://telescoper.blog/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/s7gjcutw88o71.jpg?w=450" src="https://telescoper.blog/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/s7gjcutw88o71.jpg?w=450" alt="" class="wp-image-81912" srcset="https://telescoper.blog/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/s7gjcutw88o71.jpg?w=450 450w, https://telescoper.blog/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/s7gjcutw88o71.jpg?w=900 900w, https://telescoper.blog/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/s7gjcutw88o71.jpg?w=125 125w, https://telescoper.blog/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/s7gjcutw88o71.jpg?w=249 249w, https://telescoper.blog/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/s7gjcutw88o71.jpg?w=768 768w, https://telescoper.blog/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/s7gjcutw88o71.jpg?w=850 850w" sizes="(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px" /></a></figure>
