<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Next, published on Wednesday 11th February in the folder <a href="https://astro.theoj.org/section/1189-astrophysics-of-galaxies">Astrophysics of Galaxies</a>, is &#8220;<a href="https://astro.theoj.org/article/157554-interpreting-nebular-emission-lines-in-the-high-redshift-universe">Interpreting nebular emission lines in the high-redshift Universe</a>&#8221; by Aswin P. Vijayan (U. Sussex, UK) and 9 others based in the UK, Taiwan, China and The Netherlands. This article examines the reliability of diagnostics used to estimate star formation rate and gas-phase oxygen abundance in high-redshift galaxies. It finds that variations in stellar populations and star-dust geometry. The overlay is here:</p>


<div class="wp-block-image">
<figure class="aligncenter size-large"><a href="https://telescoper.blog/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/vijaya_overlay.jpg"><img loading="lazy" width="1024" height="576" data-attachment-id="81874" data-permalink="https://telescoper.blog/2026/02/14/weekly-update-from-the-open-journal-of-astrophysics-14-02-2026/vijaya_overlay/" data-orig-file="https://telescoper.blog/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/vijaya_overlay.jpg" data-orig-size="1920,1080" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}" data-image-title="Vijaya_overlay" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://telescoper.blog/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/vijaya_overlay.jpg?w=300" data-large-file="https://telescoper.blog/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/vijaya_overlay.jpg?w=450" src="https://telescoper.blog/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/vijaya_overlay.jpg?w=1024" alt="" class="wp-image-81874" srcset="https://telescoper.blog/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/vijaya_overlay.jpg?w=1024 1024w, https://telescoper.blog/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/vijaya_overlay.jpg?w=150 150w, https://telescoper.blog/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/vijaya_overlay.jpg?w=300 300w, https://telescoper.blog/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/vijaya_overlay.jpg?w=768 768w, https://telescoper.blog/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/vijaya_overlay.jpg?w=1440 1440w, https://telescoper.blog/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/vijaya_overlay.jpg 1920w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></a></figure>
